  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "小朋友们好！欢迎来到分数可视化实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.72,
      "size": 43488,
      "text": "你有没有分过蛋糕？把一个蛋糕切成几块，每人拿一块，这就是分数的来源！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "今天，我们要用漂亮的图形来学习分数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.22,
      "size": 19440,
      "text": "准备好了吗？让我们开始吧！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "分数由两部分组成：上面的数叫分子，下面的数叫分母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "分母告诉我们把整体分成了多少份。比如分母是4，就是分成4份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "分子告诉我们取了其中的几份。比如分子是1，就是取了1份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "所以四分之一，就是把整体分成4份，取其中的1份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-5",
      "filename": "concept-concept-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/concept-concept-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "看饼图！蓝色部分就是我们取的那一份，灰色部分是剩下的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-1",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.19,
      "size": 19008,
      "text": "分数可以用不同的图形来表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-2",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "饼图就像切蛋糕，把圆形分成几块。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-3",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "条形图就像巧克力棒，把长条分成几段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-4",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "网格图就像格子纸，把方块分成几个小格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-5",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/visualization-vis-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "不管用哪种图形，表示的分数都是一样的！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-1",
      "filename": "compare-compare-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/compare-compare-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.42,
      "size": 22752,
      "text": "现在来学习怎么比较两个分数的大小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-2",
      "filename": "compare-compare-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/compare-compare-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "看图最直观！哪个分数涂色的部分更多，哪个就更大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-3",
      "filename": "compare-compare-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/compare-compare-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "比如四分之一和三分之二，三分之二涂色更多，所以三分之二更大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-4",
      "filename": "compare-compare-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/compare-compare-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.16,
      "size": 50544,
      "text": "也可以把分数变成小数来比较。四分之一等于0.25，三分之二约等于0.67。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-5",
      "filename": "compare-compare-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/compare-compare-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "0.67大于0.25，所以三分之二大于四分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-1",
      "filename": "addition-add-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/addition-add-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "分数加法有一个小技巧：先通分，再相加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-2",
      "filename": "addition-add-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/addition-add-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.48,
      "size": 23616,
      "text": "通分就是把两个分数变成相同的分母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-3",
      "filename": "addition-add-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/addition-add-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "比如四分之一加三分之二，公共分母是4乘3等于12。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-4",
      "filename": "addition-add-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/addition-add-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "四分之一变成十二分之三，三分之二变成十二分之八。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-5",
      "filename": "addition-add-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/addition-add-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "分子相加：3加8等于11。结果是十二分之十一！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-1",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/multiplication-mul-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "分数乘法比加法简单！分子乘分子，分母乘分母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-2",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/multiplication-mul-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.08,
      "size": 17280,
      "text": "比如四分之一乘三分之二。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-3",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/multiplication-mul-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "分子：1乘2等于2。分母：4乘3等于12。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-4",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/multiplication-mul-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "结果是十二分之二，约分后是六分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-5",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/multiplication-mul-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22320,
      "text": "分数乘法的意思是\"取一部分的一部分\"。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-1",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/simplify-simp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "约分就是把分数变得更简单，但大小不变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-2",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/simplify-simp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "方法是：找到分子和分母的最大公约数，然后同时除以它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-3",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/simplify-simp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "比如十二分之四，4和12的最大公约数是4。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-4",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/simplify-simp-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "分子4除以4等于1，分母12除以4等于3。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-5",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/simplify-simp-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.59,
      "size": 41472,
      "text": "所以十二分之四约分后是三分之一。看图，它们涂色的面积是一样的！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-1",
      "filename": "parameters-param-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/parameters-param-1.mp3",
      "duration": 0.84,
      "size": 13392,
      "text": "现在轮到你来试试了！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-2",
      "filename": "parameters-param-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/parameters-param-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "在右边的控制面板，你可以选择不同的操作：比较、加法、乘法或约分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-3",
      "filename": "parameters-param-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/parameters-param-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "拖动滑块可以改变分子和分母。看看图形会怎么变化？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-4",
      "filename": "parameters-param-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/parameters-param-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.52,
      "size": 40320,
      "text": "试试切换不同的图形：饼图、条形图、网格图，哪个最容易理解？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-5",
      "filename": "parameters-param-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/parameters-param-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "多试几组数字，你会发现分数的规律！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.19,
      "size": 19008,
      "text": "分数在生活中到处都能用到！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "分蛋糕、分披萨，每人拿几分之几。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "看时间，半小时就是一小时的二分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/application-app-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "打折促销，打五折就是原价的二分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-5",
      "filename": "application-app-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/application-app-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "学好分数，你就能解决很多生活中的问题啦！"
    },
    {
